text: It is a small shopping mall but it has a lot of variety. There are many types of food to choose from and there are practical shops such as Owndays, Guardian and Fairprice. It has a bakery as well. Despite its humble size, you can get many things done here! They also often have booths.
Great place to buy daily stuff. Having a big FairPrice, Hawker center, and many more shops.

I been near numerous time and finding shops is always challenging but my biggest turn off is the cleanliness. Luckily the colour of the tile is grey but if you look closely it’s obviously dirty. I won’t comment on the toilet … but seems the building management have super low budget on maintenance and cleaning
Z1 beauty- Newly opened 1 stop beauty zone , with nail medi and pedicure,  and facial wash and even normal hair wash or scalp treatment available . Definitely worth a try
We often go there for grocery shopping or buying food. This mall has less value now due to opening of bukit batok wesg hawker center. Though they have NTUC with fresh items and a barber place
